p.s. I dont cast KEI anymore for anything less than 100 pp.  I did donations for a while and while i have earned close to 25k from donations I get more than aggravated with people like you who choose to abuse the service I am providing.  Time after time I get stiffed and people are like 'but you said donations'  Well fine. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  now I do not do it for donations.  I do it for 100 pp per person.  Keeps the people from bugging me, and lets me go out and level and raid.  Expecting compensation for the only 3 - 4 hour superbuff in the game (for casters), allowing them to PL themselves is not greed based, it is market driven.  Your pathetic whining makes me sick.<br>
